Ably,is,a,hosted,real,time,messaging,service,for,web,enabled,devices,The,subscription,based,service,provides,a,scalable,fast,and,secure,solution,for,connecting,any,Internet,enabled,device,or,app,to,any,other,device,or,server,in,milliseconds,The,Ably,REST,API,provides,a,way,for,a,wide,range,of,server,and,client,devices,to,communicate,with,the,Ably,service,API,functions,include,authentication,publication,of,messages,retrieval,of,message,history,retrieval,of,presence,state,and,presence,and,retrieval,of,statistics,for,application,usage